 {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nExtends Account Cash Discount Base and Payment Order modules to let you\nadd invoices on payment order considering the cash discount on it.\nWhen an invoice with cash discount is added to a payment order,\nthe amount proposed on payment line will be the residual amount discount deducted,\nprovided that the due date has not expired.\n\nThis module also offers to search by discount due date to add invoices on\npayment order and add discount amount on payment line.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/account-payment/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/account-payment/issues/new?body=module:%20account_cash_discount_payment%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- ACSONE SA/NV\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Christelle De Coninck (ACSONE) \\<<mailto:christelle.deconinck@acsone.eu>>\n- St\u00e9phane Bidoul (ACSONE) \\<<mailto:stephane.bidoul@acsone.eu>>\n- Adrien Peiffer (ACSONE) \\<<mailto:adrien.peiffer@acsone.eu>>\n- Benjamin Willig (ACSONE) \\<<mailto:benjamin.willig@acsone.eu>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/account-payment](https://github.com/OCA/account-payment/tree/14.0/account_cash_discount_payment) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models.account_move", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models..account_move", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models.account_move_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models..account_move_line", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models.account_payment_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models..account_payment_line", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models.account_move_line", "documentation": ["Copyright 2018 ACSONE SA/NV", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models.account_move_line.AccountMoveLine", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models.account_move_line.AccountMoveLine._prepare_payment_line_vals", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "payment_order", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models.account_move_line.AccountMoveLine._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models.account_move_line.AccountMoveLine.discount_due_date", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_cash_discount_payment.models.account_move_line.AccountMoveLine.discount_amount", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "inst